cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with a Computer Vision problem of future video prediction, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new architecture for recurrent auto-encoders, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new type of Gated Recurrent Units, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper uses neural networks for its proposed architecture, which is a subfield of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on three video datasets, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
